The project has three LangGraph workflows:
  - app/workflows/rms_workflow/
  - app/workflows/hrms_workflow/
  - app/workflows/material_workflow/

Task 4 will rewrite parts of these workflows to:
  - Replace the keyword-based intent classifier with an LLM-driven
    classifier that returns BOTH collection and persona.
  - Wire Gate 2 (per-agent permission check) into permission nodes.
  - Load agent configs (system_prompt, allowed_tools, model_name)
    from the dpah_agents table instead of hardcoded values.
  - Remove the 24 legacy references to `collection_agents` and
    similar fat-JWT patterns that survive in workflow files.

